{"tid":2335854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《華爾街日報》引消息：中國科興疫苗　巴西測試有效率高於 50% 門檻","createTime":"2020-12-22T07:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T12:01:57.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5105d9569ff91ef56796c0506cf7de7d5b9805a2","tid":2335854,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:36:40.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》引消息：中國科興疫苗　巴西測試有效率高於 50% 門檻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E9%AB%98%E6%96%BC-50-%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB/?fbclid=IwAR1H90nonBDTiga5lJN_LgdkhMNMejkeGKuMVwLoBZhzbQ-f_gxuOlR-tPg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%25A1%2597%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%2588%2588%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597-%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2595%2588%25E7%258E%2587%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2596%25BC-50-%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25AA%25BB%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1H90nonBDTiga5lJN_LgdkhMNMejkeGKuMVwLoBZhzbQ-f_gxuOlR-tPg&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FUngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=81e128ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%25A1%2597%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%2588%2588%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597-%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2595%2588%25E7%258E%2587%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2596%25BC-50-%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25AA%25BB%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1H90nonBDTiga5lJN_LgdkhMNMejkeGKuMVwLoBZhzbQ-f_gxuOlR-tPg&h=282d0acc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E9%AB%98%E6%96%BC-50-%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB/?fbclid=IwAR1H90nonBDTiga5lJN_LgdkhMNMejkeGKuMVwLoBZhzbQ-f_gxuOlR-tPg</a><br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》周一（21 日）引述有參與開發人士消息指，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">中國科興生物的武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) 疫苗已在巴西的第 3 階段臨床測試有效率高於 50%</span></span></strong> ，即高於有效防護力門檻，換言之各國監管機構可對該疫苗使用開綠燈。<br />\n<br />\n港府有採購  預料最先到港  <br />\n<br />\n科興生物研發的的武肺疫苗，名為 CoronaVac（「克爾來福」滅活疫苗），巴西是首個完成該款疫苗第 3 階段臨床測試國家，該疫苗還在印尼和土耳其進行測試。港府目前訂購或有協議的武漢肺炎疫苗當中，預計最先到港的一款，正是由內地科興研製的「克爾來福」滅活疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n由於中國聲稱 COVID-19 在當地基本上受控制，中國疫苗製造商於是在國外進行臨床測試。報道引述該開發人士表示，第 3 階段臨床測試結果顯示克爾來福的有效防護力超過 50％ ，這是國際科學家認為該疫苗有效的門檻，但他拒絕提供任何進一步消息。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">有追踪該疫苗發展的學家則表示，希望「克爾來福」能顯示出與其他 COVID-19 疫苗相似的效用，例如輝瑞、 Moderna 等的疫苗均提供 94% 以上的有效防護力。</span></span></strong>報道引述巴西聖保羅大學醫學院教授艾維斯（Domingos Alves）指出，期望該款疫苗的有效率高於九成。他又指出，疫苗首階段的測試結果「非常好」。"},{"pid":"ec301ee425b7958cf1a143df059a5f4ebf961be4","tid":2335854,"uid":169801,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:40:19.000Z","msg":"唔怪得人地印度70％都公報，支那唔敢公報，又唔敢強制全民種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02118a78e9d9d6562700af9048ead30cd6954e18","tid":2335854,"uid":277702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec301ee425b7958cf1a143df059a5f4ebf961be4","tid":2335854,"uid":169801,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:40:19.000Z","msg":"唔怪得人地印度70％都公報，支那唔敢公報，又唔敢強制全民種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:47:52.000Z","msg":"價錢重要貴唔止一倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65cced5feb19fd85cfb03bc6a9c918cf9acdf3bd","tid":2335854,"uid":145923,"like":6,"dislike"